{"word":"ἀνθοβολέω","slug":"ἀνθοβολέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνθοβολέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἀνθόβολος'><el>ἀνθόβολος</el></a>\n<p/><i>to bestrew with flowers</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b>:— <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to have flowers showered upon one</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/>"}]}